              "subtype": "action_type",
              "type": "stat_block_section"
            },
            "effect": "The cultist flies into a frenzy that lasts 1 minute. While frenzied, the cultist gains a +1 status bonus to attack rolls and a +2 status bonus to damage rolls, and they take a \u20132 penalty to AC. The cultist can't voluntarily stop their frenzy. After their frenzy, the cultist is fatigued.",
